        <updateDate>2013-07-22T13:44:29Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Preventing Unionization of Revenue Service Employees Act or the PURSE Act - Excludes employees of the Internal Revenue Service (IRS) from provisions of federal personnel law allowing federal employees to organize, bargain collectively, and participate in labor organizations. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
